  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When someone performs an action in your app’s interface, create a matching app intent and donate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "it to the system. Donations help the system analyze a person’s current actions and predict their future"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "actions. For example, if someone asks your app for the weather each morning, the system might",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "proactively suggest the same action each morning. Restrict your donations to direct interactions"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "with your app’s interface, and not to interactions started by Siri or the Shortcuts app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can also improve the quality of your app’s searchable content by donating app entities to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the system. Donate entities to Spotlight with the rest of your app’s content so the system can",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "use them to display content directly in your app. In your app’s interface, associate entities with"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "views to communicate the data your app currently shows. Apple Intelligence and Siri use your"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "donations to improve conversational results.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
